        "created_at": "2004-08-08T17:34:27.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"&quot;&quot;Atresica&quot;&quot;\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n \"\"Atresica\"\":</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>For gods sake O_bras, just because we dont post doesnt mean we dont notice.</p>\n<p>Or did you forget you can see the amount of views of the post?</p>\n<p>Bumping is not allowed on this forum unless having a good reason, this is NOT a good reason. Not to mention that your post has been bumped 3 hours after the post, at a time where most forum members (considdering most live here in Europe or the Middle East) are asleep.<br>\nPlease be a bit considerant and wait for replies, this kind of attentionseeking only puts people off.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Youre right. Ill not do this anymore. OK?</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"&quot;&quot;ChaosFish&quot;&quot;\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n \"\"ChaosFish\"\":</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Obras: you can send him a link to Little Bit Adventure, this is basically what the site is for.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I already explained him, how to use the programs, some of the game has already been translated; see the sceenshots. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
