        "created_at": "2005-03-16T16:23:17.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>News:<br>\nI contacted that Korean guy again, and now Im going to re-do the font a bit (make the characters fatter). In meanwhile, he also thought about a LBA 1 translation, which he is going to start making as soon, as the LBA 2 translation is done. And when hell finish the LBA 1 translation, too, Ill try to convince him to join our team for our Big project.</p>\n<p>Also, for time being, he doesnt want to join any forums at all, not even the MBN, so for information.</p>",
